    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "While working in a ``pcode`` module for Julia I noticed this bad behavior of the the pen setting of ``grdview.'s -T`` option\r\n\r\n```\r\ngmt grdview lixo.grd -R-3.15/3.15/-3.15/3.15 -JX14c/0 -Baf -n+a -T+s+o2,dash -Clixo.cpt -png lixo\r\n```\r\n[files.zip](https://github.com/GenericMappingTools/gmt/files/8105220/files.zip)\r\n![lixo](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/537321/154870551-8d70d1fe-95aa-4b9e-9824-5d95f92e1a69.png)\r\n\r\n",
